Class GameStateData

java.lang.Object
cz.cvut.fel.pjv.dungeon_escape.model.GameStateData
public class GameStateData extends Object
Contains serializable game state data for saving/loading functionality. Stores critical player and game progress information that needs to persist between sessions.
